WEBVTT

00:03:59.000 --> 00:04:01.696
I've known this my whole life,
I've hid it from everyone,

00:04:01.720 --> 00:04:03.016
but I can't do it anymore.

00:04:03.040 --> 00:04:05.816
My wife's supportive,
I can financially afford it,

00:04:05.840 --> 00:04:07.336
I've got to make these changes.

00:04:07.360 --> 00:04:10.880
Please consider me,
and let's evaluate me for HRT."

00:04:11.600 --> 00:04:13.736
The doctor said,
"We can't do anything today.

00:04:13.760 --> 00:04:15.320
You need to go get an HIV test."

00:04:17.160 --> 00:04:18.360
She couldn't believe it.

00:04:19.160 --> 00:04:20.375
She was furious.

00:04:20.399 --> 00:04:22.200
She was angry. She was disappointed.

00:04:23.040 --> 00:04:26.896
If her doctor treated her this way,
how would the rest of the world treat her?

00:04:26.920 --> 00:04:29.296
First, he wouldn't shake her hand,

00:04:29.320 --> 00:04:32.456
and second, when he heard
she was transgender,